text:
I was being recommended to this bookstore as my partner bought a few books from them.
Books prices ranges from $1-10 and it's such a steal with lots of genres to choose from- they accept card payment too
Textbook, stationary, sch essential, go scout what you need here. They accept digital payment already hahaha.
There are various books in Chinese and English. Especially our Nanyang Publishing House has a long-term and happy cooperation with this store.
